<BaseLayout
  title="Portable Conveyors: Mobile Belt, Roller & Telescoping Units for Dock Loading"
  description="Complete guide to portable conveyors: mobile belt conveyors, telescoping units, wheeled frames, dock loading, battery power, and selection for warehouse and temporary conveying operations."
